show.description: Maids Plan is a dramatic family thriller about greed, betrayal, and hidden agendas. When Rani, a maid in the wealthy Hinduja household, uncovers secrets of theft, lies, and lust within the mansion, she becomes both a pawn and a player in a dangerous game. But as the staff secretly plot to usurp the empire, loyalties are tested, and one shocking twist could turn servants into masters.
